Log for Run 003: MF88 Individual Supply + Central Exhaust (SZHP)  /  Standard 

CSE 0.928.0 for Win32 console



Input for Run 002: MF88 Individual Supply + Central Exhaust (SZHP)  /  Standar

        
        ALTER  DHWSYS  "dhwsys-DHW Heat Pump"
           ALTER  DHWHEATER  "dhwhtr1-t24std-CHPWH"
              whVolRunning = @DHWSYS["dhwsys-DHW Heat Pump"].volRunningDes
              whHeatingCap = @DHWSYS["dhwsys-DHW Heat Pump"].heatingCapDes
        endDHWSYS
        
         UNSET verbose         // re-enable progress messages
        
        ALTER DHWSYS   "dhwsys-DHW Heat Pump"  
         ALTER DHWLOOPHEATER   "dhwlphtr-DHW Heat Pump"  
           whTEx = ($tDbO + 70) / 2             // Temperature surrounding tank (currently active only for ASHPX model, when no whZone specified), °F
        
         ALTER DHWHEATER   "dhwhtr1-t24std-CHPWH"  
           whTEx = ($tDbO + 70) / 2             // Temperature surrounding tank (currently active only for ASHPX model, when no whZone specified), °F
           whASHPSrcT = $tDbO                   // Temperature source for compressor (currently active only for ASHPX model, when no whASHPSrcZn specified), °F
        
        ALTER DHWSYS   "dhwsys-F1 Business Center"  
